### Register User for Event
POST http://localhost:3000/api/registrations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "event-id-123",
  "userId": "user-id-123",
  "ticketIds": ["ticket-id-1", "ticket-id-2"]
}

###

### Get Registration by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/registrations/{{registrationId}}

###

### Update Registration
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/registrations/{{registrationId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "confirmed"
}

###

### Delete Registration
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/registrations/{{registrationId}}

###

### Get All Registrations for User
GET http://localhost:3000/api/registrations/user/{{userId}}

###
